These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
There 4 different types of food: lemon, orange, eggplant, mango
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person eating mango is between the person eating orange and the person eating eggplant##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| Food     | lemon     | eggplant | mango  | orange      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
City: colone, nizza, edinburgh, boston
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| City   | colone | nizza    | boston     | edinburgh  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
House: wooden, modern, futuristic, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the wooden house is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| House           | modern | townhouse | futuristic | wooden  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bus, car, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person driving the car##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Transport   | bus  | boat   | taxi  | car |

