.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard, police-officer, lawyer
1. the nurse is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the security-guard##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the police-officer##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the security-guard is on the left or right of the police-officer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | fishing | filmmaking | board-games | drawing   |
| Job   | security-guard | police-officer | nurse      | lawyer |

