.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, tea, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, russian
1. the argentine is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the russian and the chinese##2
3. the person drinking cola is the chinese##1
4. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | fanta | cola | tea      | soy-milk   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | chinese    | argentine | russian |

