.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, filmmaking, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts, western, drama
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
5. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
6. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | card-games | filmmaking | writing    | chess      |
| Movie-Genre   | western       | drama       | martial-arts | fantasy |

