4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | epic  | zombie | animation |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

