1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Transport      | motorbike | quad-bike    | van  | subway |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | dubstep | indie | punk  |

